When changing from Language to number format to supoort for all logon language since every language cannot be hardcoded. 


2.	Replace the function module DATE_TO_DAY with DAY_IN_WEEK 
3.	Pass Existing input P_DATE and get the output as Number. 
4.	Replacing the EN hard coded value with the following
From Sunday    to 7.
From Monday   to 1.
From Tuesday   to 2.
From Wed.        to 3.
From Thursday to 4.
From Friday      to 5.
From Sat.          to 6.

